<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />你送过来的<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那个圣诞老人给我的礼物，
里面其实装着<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特别可爱的玩具哦！<delay40 />
看到后感觉心里暖洋洋的呢～<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圣诞节真的好棒呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我太高兴能收到圣诞老人的礼物了，<delay20 />
昨天一直兴奋个没完呢，<delay8 />
晚上都没怎么睡好～！
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是<tag a="110" b="4" />你把礼物
送到我手上这件事也成为了<delay20 />
我的一段宝贵回忆哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天能和你交换礼物真是太高兴了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经看过我给你的礼物了吗？
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这可是我为了<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
费尽千辛万苦才选出来的，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可要好好爱惜它呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />荣获我心目中<delay20 /><tag a="90" b="27" />年<delay8 />
平安夜快乐回忆奖的是<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
交换礼物这件事～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />恭喜你，<tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年也要和我交换礼物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />争取得奖哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />托<tag a="110" b="4" />的福，<delay20 />
昨天的平安夜，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我过得真是太满足了～！
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />帮助圣诞老人送礼物明明已经有够忙的了，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你却还特地过来和我交换礼物。<delay8 />
真是太感谢你了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天不光从圣诞老人那儿，<delay20 />
我还从<tag a="110" b="4" />你这里
收到了礼物，<delay8 />真是最棒的一天了～
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天这个圣诞节，<delay20 />
我打算一边细品昨天的余味，<delay8 />
一边悠闲度过呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天的平安夜<delay8 />过得如何呀～？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我过得还蛮开心的呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，我其实很想和
<tag a="110" b="4" />你交换礼物来着，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来这个乐趣只能留到明年了呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
昨天的平安夜<delay20 />你过得开心吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我昨天吃了超好吃的蛋糕哦！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实<delay8 />我还买了一个蛋糕，
准备用来庆祝今天的圣诞节呢。<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我过会儿就要去享用它了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
